msgstr "谢谢你！"

#: src/flavors/cycle1/_config.translations.py:42
msgid ""
"Thank you for sharing your idea with us! Please fill out the short form "
"below. Only the information you choose to display will be made public."
msgstr "感谢您与我们分享您的想法！请填写下方的简短表格。只有您选择显示的信息才会公开。"

#: src/flavors/cycle1/_config.translations.py:43
#: src/flavors/cycle2/_config.translations.py:47
#: src/flavors/cycle3/_config.translations.py:48
