msgstr "设施、公园和娱乐  "

#: src/flavors/cycle1/_config.translations.py:72
msgid "Are you submitting this idea as part of a community event?"
msgstr "您是否将此想法作为社区活动的一部分提交？"

#: src/flavors/cycle1/_config.translations.py:73
msgid "No event; I am submitting this idea on my own"
msgstr "没有活动；我自己提交这个想法"

#: src/flavors/cycle1/_config.translations.py:74
msgid ""
"Yes, at an Idea Collection Workshop hosted by an organization sponsored by "
"the Office of Participatory Budgeting"
msgstr "是的，在由参与式预算办公室赞助的组织主办的创意收集研讨会上"

#: src/flavors/cycle1/_config.translations.py:75
msgid "Yes, at an independent community gathering"
msgstr "是的，在独立的社区聚会上"

